Program: Last Word
Title: 18/12/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00p99n1
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 20 Dec 2009
Matthew Bannister presents the obituary series, analysing and celebrating the life stories of people who have recently died. The programme reflects on people of distinction and interest from many walks of life, some famous and some less well known. Marking the lives of Paul Samuelson, Yegor Gaidar, Bobby Jaye, Sir John Quicke and Ken Wlaschin. Show less